--><p><lb
n="1"/>valkhāḥ paramabhaṭṭāraka-pādānuddhyāto mahārāja-bhuluṇḍaḥ samājñāpayati sa<lb
n="2" break="no"/>
rvvān evāsmat-santakān āyuktakān
</p>
<p>vijñātam astu vaḥ samanujānīmo <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>sya valkhā<lb
n="3" break="no"/>
dhiṣṭhāna-vāstavya-nānā-gotra-vrata-caraṇa-tapaḥ-svādhyāyopetasyārya-cāturvvai<lb
n="4" break="no"/>
dyasya narmmadāyāḥ dakṣiṇa-taṭe bappabhaṭṭi-bhuktau rāma-vijñāpyān nimbapadrakan nā<lb
n="5" break="no"/>
ma grāmaṁ brahmadeyam ācandrā<sic>rk</sic>a-tārakā-kālīnam anvaya-bhojyaṁ bhogāyaivam i<lb
n="6" break="no"/>
dānīm asyāsmābhiḥ kr̥tānujñasyocitayā brahmadeya-bhuktyā bhuñjataḥ kr̥<lb
n="7" break="no"/>
ṣataḥ samāvāsayataś ca sarvvair evāsmat-pakṣa-tat-kulyādibhiḥ samanuma<lb
n="8" break="no"/>
ntavyaṁ</p>
<p>Arakṣika-haṭaka-dūtakaḥ</p>
<p>varṣe <num value="107"><unclear><g type="numeral">100</g></unclear> 7</num> caitra śu <num value="2">2</num><!--
L8 RT read the date as 57, but it is very probably 107. See Balogh_Kiss_2019.
--></p>


